overview: March 20th, 2017 :: WhatCulture Pro Wrestling presents Bulletproof from Bowlers Exhibition Centre in Manchester, England. Matches include: • WCPW Tag Team Title Texas Tornado Match The Swords Of Essex (Scott Wainwright & Will Ospreay) (c) vs. Liam Slater & Matt Riddle vs. The Young Bucks (Matt Jackson & Nick Jackson) vs. Prospect (Alex Gracie & Lucas Archer) • Rampage vs. Drake • Viper (w/Bea Priestley) vs. Lana Austin • WCPW Women's Title Match Bea Priestley (w/Viper) (c) vs. Tessa Blanchard • Elimination Match Doug Williams vs. El Ligero vs. Ricochet vs. Marty Scurll vs. Martin Kirby vs. BT Gunn vs. Travis Banks • WCPW Internet Title #1 Contendership Match Joe Hendry vs. Gabriel Kidd • ROH World Title Match Christopher Daniels (c) vs. Zack Sabre Jr. vs. Adam Cole • WCPW World Title Match Drew Galloway (c) vs. Joe Coffey
title: WCPW Bulletproof
